</taxonomicName>
sp. nov. (ex-type FMR 17659). 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">A-C</emphasis>
Colonies on PDA, PCA and OA, respectively, at 25 °C after 7 d 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">D-H</emphasis>
